# Portfolio repository allowlist
# Raw project folders, zip backups, datasets, weights, and run outputs stay local.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/docs/
!/docs/**
!/portfolio-projects/
!/portfolio-projects/**
!/projects/
!/projects/**

# Safety exclusions inside allowed folders
**/.idea/
**/__pycache__/
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/runs/
**/wandb/
**/weights/
**/train/images/
**/valid/images/
**/val/images/
**/test/images/
**/train/labels/
**/valid/labels/
**/val/labels/
**/test/labels/
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
*.engine
*.pkl
*.npy
*.npz
*.pyc
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z
*.mp4
*.avi
*.mov
*.mkv
*.bmp
